  "key": "B minor",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "I feel you in me, can't be your bad day As we're losing, this time we'll fall apart I know we'll be stronger for it, baby we're losing I'm out here, hopefully time will make us Prouder than we think we can of And our love, it won't burn, no It's prouder than we stand here And our love just won't burn Oh, what do we do when it all goes Down away in the sadness Oh, do we try a little bit more? I know I say that a lot, but I'm always trying to be more And you could help with dreaming, even if we continue this streak And I don't think of me, we're just doomed in the room Ain't nothing to say, cause I thought it and I said it all But baby, calm down to a different thought Oh yeah, we'll calm down together And we'll get out of this drug mess we made This whole mess we made And everything that we thought was alright It turns out it's not for you To decide or judge any other of the people here I know there's a little bit more Between our clean nights, come on home You're not alone in the wonders of it all, just come back home I promise not to let you speak your name And I'm praying for the end of all of our pain I'm praying that you remember The name we made for ourselves But if it's gotta go Maybe I'm allowed to watch it go",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 23.15999984741211,
      "text": "I feel you in me, can't be your bad day As we're losing, this time we'll fall apart",
      "start": 7.360000133514404
    },
    {
      "end": 29.1200008392334,
      "text": "I know we'll be stronger for it, baby we're losing",
      "start": 23.15999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 39.70000076293945,
      "text": "I'm out here, hopefully time will make us Prouder than we think we can of",
      "start": 29.1200008392334
    },
    {
      "end": 49.15999984741211,
      "text": "And our love, it won't burn, no It's prouder than we stand here",
      "start": 40.099998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 53.619998931884766,
      "text": "And our love just won't burn",
      "start": 49.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 62.439998626708984,
      "text": "Oh, what do we do when it all goes Down away in the sadness",
      "start": 53.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 67.9000015258789,
      "text": "Oh, do we try a little bit more?",
      "start": 62.439998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 74.26000213623047,
      "text": "I know I say that a lot, but I'm always trying to be more",
      "start": 68.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 79.72000122070312,
      "text": "And you could help with dreaming, even if we continue this streak",
      "start": 74.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 85.54000091552734,
      "text": "And I don't think of me, we're just doomed in the room",
      "start": 79.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 90.5,
      "text": "Ain't nothing to say, cause I thought it and I said it all",
      "start": 85.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 95.16000366210938,
      "text": "But baby, calm down to a different thought",
      "start": 90.5
    },
    {
      "end": 98.63999938964844,
      "text": "Oh yeah, we'll calm down together",
      "start": 95.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 101.9800033569336,
      "text": "And we'll get out of this drug mess we made",
      "start": 98.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 104.5199966430664,
      "text": "This whole mess we made",
      "start": 101.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 108.73999786376953,
      "text": "And everything that we thought was alright",
      "start": 104.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 113.37999725341797,
      "text": "It turns out it's not for you",
      "start": 108.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 118.62000274658203,
      "text": "To decide or judge any other of the people here",
      "start": 113.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 123.05999755859375,
      "text": "I know there's a little bit more",
      "start": 118.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 131.6999969482422,
      "text": "Between our clean nights, come on home",
      "start": 123.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 140.75999450683594,
      "text": "You're not alone in the wonders of it all, just come back home",
      "start": 132.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 144.8800048828125,
